Commentary Text: Bhuvneshwar to Y Pathan, out Y Pathan Run Out!! The ball jagged back in and Pathan missed the heave. The ball thudded the back pad and went away towards the bowler. Yusuf unaware of it, looked for a suicidal single. But Bhuvi in his his followthrough gathered it and flicked it onto the sticks to catch him short. This is tragedy for KKR. He was in no position to take a single. Y Pathan run out (Bhuvneshwar) 0(1)

Commentary Text: Bhuvneshwar to Chris Lynn, out Caught by Naman Ojha!! Full and swinging away, the batsman backed away to jam it. He thudded the bat onto the ground but the ball chalked the bottom part of the willow on the way. The on-field umpire went upstairs who had a look and gave it in favour of the bowler. Bhuvi does it again for SRH. Chris Lynn c Naman Ojha b Bhuvneshwar 6(2) [6s-1]
